SpaceTraders - Outfitting

p
Game Concepts

h1
Outfitting

p
Work in Progress

p
This feature is in active development and may not be fully implemented.

p
Ship modules and mounts can be installed to increase the capabilities of your ships.

p
Increasing your reputation with a faction will unlock more modules and mounts for purchase.

p
The frame, engine and reactor of your ship cannot be removed or swapped.

p
Your frame determines the number of module slots and mounts available on your ship.

p
Your engines determine the speed of your ship.

p
Your reactor determines the amount of power available to your ship's modules and mounts.